OpticalDistance - Class in com.lasarobotics.library.sensor.modernrobotics
Implements the Core Optical OpticalDistance Sensor with advanced methods

This sensor is only fully accurate UP TO 5 CM Different lighting conditions greatly affect distance read after 5 cm away from the object
